com.hawkejo.complexnumberfft

Interface FrequencyGenerator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FreqObservable, java.lang.Runnable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FFTFreqGen

    public interface FrequencyGenerator
extends java.lang.Runnable, FreqObservable
    An interface for an arbitrary class that computes a frequency from an array of doubles

    An interface to define any class that computes a frequency value from the specified input array or List. This interface only defines what the methods should be and what they should do rather than defining them. This class requires the ComplexNumber class as a dependency.
